MIU - MAC In Userspace
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-[Overview]---------------------------------------------------------------------
This library provides very simple mandatory access control system, based on
hijacking libc calls.

Example configuration is provided in example.conf, please, copy it to
/etc/miu.conf and modify. Remember to replace backslashes with double
backslashes! This is needed by libconfig.

-[Compilation/Installation]-----------------------------------------------------
Check if you have installed libconfig in your system, then type

  make
  cp example.conf /etc/miu.conf
  cp libmiu.so /usr/local/lib/libmiu.so
  $EDITOR /etc/miu.conf

--Testing--

  export LD_PRELOAD=/usr/local/lib/libmiu.so

then try to access files blacklisted in config.

--Install--

  echo "/usr/local/lib/libmiu.so"> /etc/ld.so.preload
